AbilityDescription.SourceString: Alternatively strike original and random target for {ATK} ATK, ignoring Reflex DEF. Repeat until Mana is exhausted. Changes target if enemy dies. Counters next incoming attack. Locks board to {Element} for {LockDuration} {LockDuration}|plural(one=turn,other=turns).
